<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Weekly AIgentable Report</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #1d4ed8);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: -40px -40px 30px -40px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .date-range {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .metrics-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .metric-card {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .metric-value {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .metric-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .metric-change {
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .metric-up {
            color: #10b981;
        }
        .metric-down {
            color: #ef4444;
        }
        .metric-neutral {
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        .section {
            margin: 30px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .top-performers {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .performer-card {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .performer-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .performer-stats {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #1d4ed8;
        }
        .insights {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border: 1px solid #0ea5e9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">AIgentable</div>
            <h1 class="title">Weekly Performance Report</h1>
            <div class="date-range">{{startDate}} - {{endDate}}</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>
            
            <p>Here's your weekly AIgentable performance summary. This report provides insights into your team's customer service activities and key metrics.</p>
            
            <div class="metrics-grid">
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-value">{{totalConversations}}</div>
                    <div class="metric-label">Total Conversations</div>
                    {{#if conversationsTrend}}
                    <div class="metric-change metric-{{conversationsTrendDirection}}">
                        {{conversationsTrend}}% vs last week
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
                
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-value">{{totalMessages}}</div>
                    <div class="metric-label">Messages Processed</div>
                    {{#if messagesTrend}}
                    <div class="metric-change metric-{{messagesTrendDirection}}">
                        {{messagesTrend}}% vs last week
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
                
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-value">{{averageResponseTime}}</div>
                    <div class="metric-label">Avg Response Time</div>
                    {{#if responseTimeTrend}}
                    <div class="metric-change metric-{{responseTimeTrendDirection}}">
                        {{responseTimeTrend}}% vs last week
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
                
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-value">{{satisfactionScore}}%</div>
                    <div class="metric-label">Customer Satisfaction</div>
                    {{#if satisfactionTrend}}
                    <div class="metric-change metric-{{satisfactionTrendDirection}}">
                        {{satisfactionTrend}}% vs last week
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if topAgents}}
            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">üèÜ Top Performing Agents</h2>
                <div class="top-performers">
                    {{#each topAgents}}
                    <div class="performer-card">
                        <div class="performer-name">{{name}}</div>
                        <div class="performer-stats">
                            {{conversations}} conversations ‚Ä¢ {{responseTime}} avg response
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    {{/each}}
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if channelBreakdown}}
            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">üìä Channel Performance</h2>
                {{#each channelBreakdown}}
                <div style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 10px; background-color: white; border-radius: 6px;">
                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
                        <span style="font-weight: bold;">{{name}}</span>
                        <span style="color: #6b7280;">{{messages}} messages</span>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background-color: #e5e7eb; height: 8px; border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 5px;">
                        <div style="background-color: #2563eb; height: 100%; width: {{percentage}}%; border-radius: 4px;"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{/each}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if insights}}
            <div class="insights">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #0369a1;">üí° Key Insights</h3>
                <ul style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                    {{#each insights}}
                    <li>{{this}}</li>
                    {{/each}}
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">View Full Dashboard</a>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>üìà Recommendations for Next Week:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                {{#if recommendations}}
                    {{#each recommendations}}
                    <li>{{this}}</li>
                    {{/each}}
                {{else}}
                <li>Continue monitoring response times to maintain customer satisfaction</li>
                <li>Review conversation patterns to identify improvement opportunities</li>
                <li>Consider additional agent training for complex queries</li>
                <li>Optimize channel-specific workflows based on performance data</li>
                {{/if}}
            </ul>
            
            <p>Thank you for using AIgentable to deliver exceptional customer service. Keep up the great work!</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>The AIgentable Analytics Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This weekly report was automatically generated based on your AIgentable activity.</p>
            <p>You can manage your report preferences in your account settings.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>